Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: Where Is the Door to the Tavern?
Description: February 11
---
Where is the door to God?

In the sound of a barking dog,

in the ring of a hammer, in a drop of rain, in the face of everyone,
everyone I see.

Where is the door to the divine tavern? Yes, in all we can behold.
